 Nation is a tour de force in the study of nationalist politics. It will be of great interest to readers concerned about Southeast Asia, Islamic politics, ethnic conflict and nationalism everywhere.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 23. Jul 2020) 0aIslam and politicsxIndonesiaxNanggroe Aceh Darussalam. 0aIslam and politicszIndonesiazAceh. 0aIslam and politicszIndonesiazNanggroe Aceh Darussalam. 0aNationalismxHistoryxIndonesiaxNanggroe Aceh Darussalam. 0aNationalismxReligious aspectsxIslam. 0aNationalismxReligious aspects. 0aNationalismzIndonesiazAcehxHistory. 0aNationalismzIndonesiazNanggroe Aceh DarussalamxHistory. 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / Terrorism.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertSUP Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013z978311070420440uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978080477627140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780804776271423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780804776271.jpg  a978-3-11-070420-4  SUP Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aGBV-deGruyter-alles